ef="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>成立了自己的经纪公司。与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rose">Rosé</a>已与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-black-label">The Black Label</a>签约。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-bang">Big Bang</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daesung">大成</a>多年来首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/big-bang-taeyang-g-dragon-daesung-reunite-seoul-concerts-3789664">再次公开了与乐队成员 G-Dragon 和太阳一起在舞台上表演的</a>感受， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/big-bang-daesung-performing-g-dragon-taeyang-pure-joy-3796413">称这种感觉是“纯粹的快乐”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gfriend-reunite-tenth-anniversary-source-music-confirms-3796450">Source Music 确认《GFRIEND》将在十周年之际重聚，</a>并首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
